header.gameNote: AARON'S AMERICAN ATHLETIC CONFERENCE MEN'S CHAMPIONSHIP - QUARTERFINAL

videos.description: Jahmal McMurray finds an open lane and drives to the basket for a reverse layup.
videos.headline: SMU's McMurray drives baseline for reverse layup

videos.description: Jahmal McMurray misses a 3-pointer but Akoy Agau is there to tip it in for a basket.
videos.headline: SMU's Agau cleans up McMurray's miss

videos.description: In the last seconds of the first half, Ben Emelogu II creates space and drains a stepback jumper.
videos.headline: SMU's Emelogu II hits jumper to close 1st half

videos.description: Off the steal, Jimmy Whitt bounces a pass to Elijah Landrum who drives to the rim for a layup.
videos.headline: SMU's Whitt connects with Landrum for layup

videos.description: Jacob Evans finds Jarron Cumberland, who drops a pass to Gary Clark for a corner 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Cincinnati ball movement leads to Clark's 3

videos.description: Ben Emelogu II drives to the rim for a layup but is met by Gary Clark who emphatically swats away the ball.
videos.headline: Cincinnati's Clark denies Emelogu II at the rim
